Claim: "A woman in black has a job."
Implication: "The woman in black reviews messages as she walks to work."
Referring expressions: Woman in black, job  Woman in black, messages, work
Formula: (exists a (exists b (IsInBlack(a) and HasJob(b))) & (forall f (forall e (  IsWalksToWork(e) ->   HasJob(f))))) -> (exists a (exists d (IsReviewsMessages(a) and IsWalksToWork(d))))
